---------- VERTICAL FORMATTING COMMANDS ---------- ,PL N  Page length N lines/page ,PG    New page ,PN N  Page number ,TF    Top of form(printer command) ,HD    Define header ,FT    Define footer ,,     End header or footer definition ,SP N  Space N lines(print parameter) ,SS N  Set spacing N sp.\line(print parameter) ,VT N  Vertical tab to Nth line(print parameter) ,VS N  Vertical spacing lines/in(print paramet.) ,NL N  Need N lines on same page